# Own the shares, rent them out. Writing the ~20-delta call after an
# oversold bounce starts collects premium while leaving room to run;
# called away means selling into strength, which is the plan working.

strategy "Covered Calls on Dips"

universe $KO

when [rsi] crosses above 35
  write [covered_call delta=20 dte=30]

close at [profit 60%]

roll at [dte 10]

risk [contracts 5]
